<HEADLINE> Umpires To Honor Chylak With Patch </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Baseball has decided to go ahead with putting a  
patch on uniforms this year -- and not those ad patches, either. 
</P>
<P>
	Baseball will honor the memory of former AL umpire Nestor  
Chylak, who will be inducted into the Hall of Fame on July 25, with 
a patch on the uniform of AL umpires. 
</P>
<P>
	Chylak, an AL umpire from 1954-78, was voted into the Hall last  
month by the Veterans' Committee. He died in 1982. 
</P>
<P>
	The patch depicts Chylak's signature over the Hall of Fame logo.  
</P>
